edu.rit.crst

Class Avalanche

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.rit.crst.Computation
      • edu.rit.crst.Test
        • edu.rit.crst.Avalanche

  • public class Avalanche
extends Test
    Class Avalanche performs an avalanche Test for a cryptographic Function. Each test data series element is the difference (bitwise exclusive-or) between the raw data series element and the first raw data series element.
    See Also:
